title: IOS Developer`
jobDescription:
We are looking for an iOS developer responsible for the development and maintenance of applications aimed at a range of iOS devices including mobile phones and tablet computers. Your primary focus will be development of iOS applications and their integration with back-end services. You will be working alongside other engineers and developers working on different layers of the infrastructure. Therefore, a commitment to collaborative problem solving, sophisticated design, and the creation of quality products is essential.

Required Skill Set:

  • Minimum 3 years of working experience in complete IOS apps development life cycle.
  • Architect, design & develop mobile applications according to specifications.
  • Proficiency in Swift and Objective-C.
  • Knowledgeable in consuming RESTful APIs to connect iOS applications to back-end services.
  • Experience in modern authorization mechanisms, such as JSON Web Token
  • Deep understanding of iOS frameworks such as Core Data and Core Animation, along with offline storage, threading, and performance tuning.
  • Experience in App security and security testing.
  • Exposure and experience in publishing App in App-Store.
  • Experience with native mobile apps IOS development, experience with database engines (MySQL, PostgreSQL, MongoDB).
  • Proficient in git
  • Experience using several 3rd party SDK frameworks such as AWS, Crashlytics, Google Maps
  • Should be independent contributor document / design / develop / test applications independently.
  • Will have to present to clients daily work hence Time-lining, documentation and communication skills should be appropriate.
